{"id":26108,"date":"2020-04-07T21:56:06","date_gmt":"2020-04-07T14:56:06","guid":{"rendered":"\/?p=26108"},"modified":"2020-04-09T12:02:44","modified_gmt":"2020-04-09T05:02:44","slug":"huong-dan-backup-website-wordpress-bang-wpvivid-pro","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"\/usecase\/huong-dan-backup-website-wordpress-bang-wpvivid-pro","title":{"rendered":"H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn &#8220;incremental backup&#8221; website WordPress v\u1edbi WPvivid Pro"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"highlight\">WordPress l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi l\u1ed7i v\u00e0 malware. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 li\u1ec7t k\u00ea h\u1ebft, nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec1u d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 website b\u1ea1n b\u1ecb DOWN kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 truy c\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. V\u00ec v\u1eady b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n backup website WordPress cho an to\u00e0n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 nhanh nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n website l\u00e0nh l\u1eb7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eeda l\u1ed7i. Sao l\u01b0u WordPress th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee9u nguy b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c cho m\u1ecdi blogger v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i lu\u00f4n \u1edf th\u1ebf ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi site b\u1ea1n \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c host tr\u00ean nh\u1eefng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd WordPress cao c\u1ea5p th\u00ec b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng r\u1ee7i ro, ch\u1ec9 kh\u00e1c m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat l\u00e0 khi \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i backup site m\u00ecnh \u1edf d\u1ea1ng \u00edt th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n nh\u01b0 m\u1ed7i tu\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n hay m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, t\u1ef1 backup v\u1eabn l\u00e0 PH\u1ea2I C\u00d3.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Do nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn n\u00ean WordPress c\u00f3 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u plugin backup WordPress \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn cho b\u1ea1n nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn. T\u00f4i tin b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean ri\u00eang cho m\u00ecnh trong \u0111\u1ea7u ho\u1eb7c \u0111ang s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean, lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 plugin backup \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u00e0 k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 server backup c\u0169ng v\u1eady. Khi \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p kh\u00e1c PH\u00d9 H\u1ee2P h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u00f4i xin gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t plugin backup \u1ed5n trong t\u1ea7m gi\u00e1 v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ed1t l\u00f5i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 <a href=\"\/out\/wpvividpro\" data-eafl-id=\"25457\" class=\"eafl-link eafl-link-text eafl-link-cloaked\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">WPvivid Pro<\/a>, m\u1ed9t phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed c\u1ee7a WPvivid tr\u00ean WordPress Repo. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng xem h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn sau!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn Incremental Backup website WordPress<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/incremental-backup.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1004\" height=\"470\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/incremental-backup.png\" alt=\"Incremental Backup\" class=\"wp-image-26153\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/incremental-backup.png 1004w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/incremental-backup-218x102.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/incremental-backup-300x140.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/incremental-backup-700x328.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/incremental-backup-768x360.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1004px) 100vw, 1004px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed, WPvivid Pro gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u chi ph\u00ed l\u01b0u tr\u1eef b\u1ea3n sao l\u01b0u. Tuy m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 plugin backup cao c\u1ea5p kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng WPvivid Pro \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u1ec1 gi\u00e1 (<a href=\"#loi-ket\">xem b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi<\/a>).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ecdi Incremental backup \u0111\u1ec1u ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 nhau, WPvivid s\u1ebd n\u00e9n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c file trong WordPress v\u00e0 database t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n l\u01b0u trong hosting v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u file zip nh\u1ecf. Sau \u0111\u00f3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh upload l\u00ean cloud m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn. Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh upload k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00e0 WPvivid s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng xo\u00e1 b\u1ea3n l\u01b0u Local tr\u00ean hosting \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng l\u01b0u l\u01b0\u1ee3ng site c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00ec b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn <a href=\"https:\/\/www.google.com\/drive\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Google Drive<\/a> ho\u1eb7c <a href=\"\/out\/pcloud\" data-eafl-id=\"22411\" class=\"eafl-link eafl-link-text eafl-link-cloaked\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer sponsored\">pCloud<\/a>. Google Drive c\u00f3 <strong>15GB<\/strong> l\u01b0u tr\u1eef mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 pCloud th\u00ec<strong> 500GB<\/strong> l\u01b0u tr\u1eef v\u1edbi tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n. \u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Google Drive l\u00e0 nhanh h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat so v\u1edbi pCloud, trong khi pCloud c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng l\u01b0u tr\u1eef v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Google Drive.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/remote-storage-trong-wpvivid-pro.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"621\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/remote-storage-trong-wpvivid-pro-1024x621.png\" alt=\"Remote Storage Trong Wpvivid Pro\" class=\"wp-image-26160\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/remote-storage-trong-wpvivid-pro-1024x621.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/remote-storage-trong-wpvivid-pro-218x132.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/remote-storage-trong-wpvivid-pro-300x182.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/remote-storage-trong-wpvivid-pro-700x424.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/remote-storage-trong-wpvivid-pro-768x465.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/remote-storage-trong-wpvivid-pro.png 1434w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>C\u00e1c Remote Storage h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 b\u1edfi WPvivid Pro hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Do zip file tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi upload l\u00ean Cloud n\u00ean t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t nhanh v\u00e0 trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m t\u00f4i c\u0169ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u00ec WPvivid kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a website. WPvivid c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tu\u1ef3 ch\u1ec9nh gi\u00fap ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh cho c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c shared hosting k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi b\u1ea1n c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t sao l\u01b0u li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u1ed7i gi\u1edd. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ed9ng cho WPvivid.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"399\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/cac-ban-sao-luu-cua-WPvivid-tren-pCloud-1024x399.png\" alt=\"Cac Ban Sao Luu Cua Wpvivid Tren Pcloud\" class=\"wp-image-26161\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/cac-ban-sao-luu-cua-WPvivid-tren-pCloud-1024x399.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/cac-ban-sao-luu-cua-WPvivid-tren-pCloud-218x85.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/cac-ban-sao-luu-cua-WPvivid-tren-pCloud-300x117.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/cac-ban-sao-luu-cua-WPvivid-tren-pCloud-700x273.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/cac-ban-sao-luu-cua-WPvivid-tren-pCloud-768x299.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/cac-ban-sao-luu-cua-WPvivid-tren-pCloud.png 1531w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption>B\u1ea3n sao l\u01b0u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia th\u00e0nh folder theo t\u1eebng ng\u00e0y<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"676\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/Ben-trong-folder-la-file-zip-1024x676.png\" alt=\"Ben Trong Folder La File Zip\" class=\"wp-image-26162\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/Ben-trong-folder-la-file-zip-1024x676.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/Ben-trong-folder-la-file-zip-218x144.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/Ben-trong-folder-la-file-zip-300x198.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/Ben-trong-folder-la-file-zip-700x462.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/Ben-trong-folder-la-file-zip-768x507.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/Ben-trong-folder-la-file-zip.png 1384w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption>M\u1ed7i folder ch\u1ee9a c\u00e1c file zip sao l\u01b0u c\u1ee7a site<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra, khi WPvivid c\u0169ng t\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t sao l\u01b0u WordPress ri\u00eang v\u1edbi database. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t sao l\u01b0u database m\u1ed7i gi\u1edd v\u00e0 WordPress m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y t\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t nhau \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u00e0i nguy\u00ean nh\u01b0 b\u0103ng th\u00f4ng ra (outbound bandwidth) v\u00e0 RAM.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/cau-hinh-incremental-backup-trong-wpvivid-pro.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"647\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/cau-hinh-incremental-backup-trong-wpvivid-pro-1024x647.png\" alt=\"Cau Hinh Incremental Backup Trong Wpvivid Pro\" class=\"wp-image-26164\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/cau-hinh-incremental-backup-trong-wpvivid-pro-1024x647.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/cau-hinh-incremental-backup-trong-wpvivid-pro-218x138.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/cau-hinh-incremental-backup-trong-wpvivid-pro-300x190.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/cau-hinh-incremental-backup-trong-wpvivid-pro-700x442.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/cau-hinh-incremental-backup-trong-wpvivid-pro-768x485.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/cau-hinh-incremental-backup-trong-wpvivid-pro.png 1309w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>C\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh cho Incremental Backup<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u00f3i th\u00eam v\u1ec1 Incremental backup, l\u00e0 d\u1ea1ng backup m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 upload nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a file m\u00e0 th\u00f4i, trong khi b\u1ea3n l\u01b0u tr\u1eef g\u1ed1c v\u1eabn gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean v\u00e0 tu\u1ef3 thu\u1ed9c theo b\u1ea1n thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp (Backup Cycle) m\u00e0 WPvivid s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea1o m\u1edbi b\u1ea3n l\u01b0u tr\u1eef g\u1ed1c theo \u0111\u00f3 (m\u1ed7i tu\u1ea7n, m\u1ed7i 2 tu\u1ea7n hay m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"tip\"><span class=\"title\">Ch\u00fa \u00dd<\/span>\n<p>Khi \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng Incremental Backup cho cloud th\u00ec s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u01b0u tr\u1eef local t\u1ea1i hosting.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i (Restore) website WordPress khi c\u1ea7n<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sao l\u01b0u s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a khi b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i website \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p site b\u1ea1n b\u1ecb l\u1ed7i nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o m\u1edbi m\u1ed9t website kh\u00e1c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i d\u1eef li\u1ec7u t\u1eeb pCloud hay Google Drive th\u00ec b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi WPvivid Pro v\u00ec b\u1ea3n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed <strong>ch\u1ec9 cho ph\u00e9p ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sao l\u01b0u c\u1ee7a site g\u1ed1c <\/strong> (sao l\u01b0u tr\u00ean cloud s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 d\u1ee5ng).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/bang-so-sanh-chuc-nang-free-va-paid-wpvividpro.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"419\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/bang-so-sanh-chuc-nang-free-va-paid-wpvividpro-1024x419.png\" alt=\"Bang So Sanh Chuc Nang Free Va Paid Wpvividpro\" class=\"wp-image-26166\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/bang-so-sanh-chuc-nang-free-va-paid-wpvividpro-1024x419.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/bang-so-sanh-chuc-nang-free-va-paid-wpvividpro-218x89.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/bang-so-sanh-chuc-nang-free-va-paid-wpvividpro-300x123.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/bang-so-sanh-chuc-nang-free-va-paid-wpvividpro-700x287.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/bang-so-sanh-chuc-nang-free-va-paid-wpvividpro-768x314.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/bang-so-sanh-chuc-nang-free-va-paid-wpvividpro.png 1351w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>B\u1ea3ng so s\u00e1nh ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a WPvivid Pro v\u00e0 WPvivid mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed <br>(ngu\u1ed3n: wpvivid.com)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi b\u1ea1n chuy\u1ec3n sang m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p hosting m\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t website m\u1edbi (k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n m\u1edbi), b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t WPvivid Pro v\u00e0 \u0111\u0103ng nh\u1eadp t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n, ch\u1ecdn b\u1ea3n sao \u0111\u00e3 l\u01b0u tr\u1eef tr\u00ean cloud v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i. C\u00e1ch l\u00e0m n\u00e0y gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang migration gi\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp th\u00f4ng qua ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u01b0u \u00fd quan tr\u1ecdng m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i hi\u1ec3u khi d\u00f9ng WPvivid Free so v\u1edbi khi d\u00f9ng b\u1ea3n Pro. B\u1ea3n Pro s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u1ef1 do v\u00e0 an to\u00e0n h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"552\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/Restore-backup-wpvivid-pro-1024x552.png\" alt=\"Restore Backup Wpvivid Pro\" class=\"wp-image-26167\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/Restore-backup-wpvivid-pro-1024x552.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/Restore-backup-wpvivid-pro-218x117.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/Restore-backup-wpvivid-pro-300x162.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/Restore-backup-wpvivid-pro-700x377.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/Restore-backup-wpvivid-pro-768x414.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/Restore-backup-wpvivid-pro.png 1312w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption>C\u00e1ch ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i sao l\u01b0u Incremental Backup<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>R\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc, WPvivid s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i khi site b\u1ea1n b\u1ecb down nh\u01b0 l\u1ed7i database. B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u ho\u1eb7c nh\u1edd tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap t\u1eeb nh\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p hosting \u0111\u1ec3 site live tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1edbi d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i c\u1ee7a WPvivid. N\u1ebfu b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1edbi th\u00ec WPvivid Pro s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i d\u1eef li\u1ec7u sao l\u01b0u (Free kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"tip\"><span class=\"title\">Ch\u00fa \u00dd<\/span>\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang d\u00f9ng WordPress multisites th\u00ec hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c to\u00e0n h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng thay v\u00ec t\u1eebng site ri\u00eang l\u1ebb.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>Staging website khi ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda hay th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t statging site lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n an to\u00e0n cho m\u1ecdi ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m ho\u1eb7c thay \u0111\u1ed5i giao di\u1ec7n, th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m plugin, c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt plugin hay thu\u00ea ng\u01b0\u1eddi develop cho site b\u1ea1n m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n x\u1ea3y ra b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 tai n\u1ea1n n\u00e0o l\u00e0m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn website hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111ang ch\u1ea1y t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t n\u00fat b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t Staging Site \u0111\u1ec3 tha h\u1ed3 v\u1ecdc v\u1ea1ch. N\u1ebfu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n xo\u00e1 Staging Site \u0111\u00f3 \u0111i v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t site kh\u00e1c. N\u1ebfu th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n b\u1ea5m n\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ee3p th\u1ec3 v\u1edbi live site hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/one-click-staging-site-trong-wpvivid-pro.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"646\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/one-click-staging-site-trong-wpvivid-pro-1024x646.png\" alt=\"One Click Staging Site Trong Wpvivid Pro\" class=\"wp-image-26169\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/one-click-staging-site-trong-wpvivid-pro-1024x646.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/one-click-staging-site-trong-wpvivid-pro-218x137.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/one-click-staging-site-trong-wpvivid-pro-300x189.png 300w, https: